                                    be used in the learning environment.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    Group work and technology e.g. Voki, Wikis, support learners to
                                    develop, reinforce and supplement lecture material, whilst
                                    developing skills in self-direction.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    Resources such as online quizzes, online learning tools, and
                                    Internet research exercises, enhance the delivery of teaching and
                                    learning and reinforce digital literacy competency.
                                </p>
                                <p>(Blended learning is, in essence, a mixture of all of the below)</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
                            <div class="panel teaching-methods">
                                <div class="normal-checkbox">
