                                    </label>
                                </div>
                                <h5 class="teachingmd-hd">Flipped Classrooms</h5>
                                <p>
                                    The typical lecture and homework elements of a course are reversed. Learners engage
                                    with the theoretical content at home e.g. via video lectures at their own pace.
                                    Educators can then maximize face-to-face/class time for concept engagement and
                                    activity based learning.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
                            <div class="panel teaching-methods">
                                <div class="normal-checkbox">
