                                    These are learning activities that actively involve learners in their learning.
                                    Students are actively involved in the learning process through acts of ‘doing’,
                                    ‘being’ and ‘critically reflecting’. Learners are encouraged to ask questions for
                                    clarification, to challenge ideas, procedures and content, to attach what is
                                    learned with skill development, and to engage in discussion with others.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
                            <div class="panel teaching-methods">
                                <div class="normal-checkbox">
                                    <label class="checkbox checkbox--material">
                                        <input autocomplete="nope" type="checkbox" class="checkbox__input checkbox--material__input">
