                                    primarily based on unique values and principles in accordance with Kaupapa Māori.
                                    Wānanga as a delivery method enhances an understanding of working in culturally
                                    appropriate ways, working with Māori, working bi-culturally, and in the application
                                    of tikanga and te reo Māori.
